1
00:00:00,770 --> 00:00:02,506
-How dare you?!

2
00:00:04,450 --> 00:00:07,152
-How dare you?

3
00:00:16,835 --> 00:00:19,134
-Hello. Welcome.

4
00:00:19,134 --> 00:00:22,264
-This is the set of
"Victorian Gentlemen."

5
00:00:22,264 --> 00:00:24,647
Streeter Seidell and I wanted
to do a sketch

6
00:00:24,647 --> 00:00:29,823
based on the taking off a glove
and slapping someone.

7
00:00:29,823 --> 00:00:32,026
-Oh, sorry.
-That one was my bad.

8
00:00:32,026 --> 00:00:34,819
Connor Storrie is a dreamboat.

9
00:00:34,819 --> 00:00:36,497
-How dare you?!

10
00:00:36,497 --> 00:00:39,469
-Very committed to character,

11
00:00:39,469 --> 00:00:42,012
very game to be silly.

12
00:00:42,012 --> 00:00:43,957
Look at your hat, Fettington.

13
00:00:43,957 --> 00:00:45,788
-Chapeau on.

14
00:00:45,788 --> 00:00:48,785
-And he's very good actor, too.

15
00:00:48,785 --> 00:00:50,350
-How dare you?

16
00:00:50,780 --> 00:00:53,662
-Are we done with this shot?
I hate it.

17
00:00:53,662 --> 00:00:56,396
-Marcello's getting punched.
-Nice.

18
00:00:56,396 --> 00:00:59,598
-Connor's getting punched.
-Oh, I'm getting punched.

19
00:00:59,598 --> 00:01:01,185
-You're getting punched.

20
00:01:01,185 --> 00:01:02,842
Everybody's getting punched.

21
00:01:02,842 --> 00:01:07,453
-We rented a dummy,
and wardrobe gave us
a second set of clothes,

22
00:01:07,453 --> 00:01:11,815
and so we were able to
not have to injure the real boy.

23
00:01:11,815 --> 00:01:15,022
-We get slapped by a dog
in this.

24
00:01:15,022 --> 00:01:18,258
No, my mustache
was falling off from moment one.

25
00:01:18,258 --> 00:01:20,515
Mustaches are annoying.

26
00:01:20,515 --> 00:01:21,949
How dare you?

27
00:01:21,949 --> 00:01:24,800
Mama!
That's it.

28
00:01:24,800 --> 00:01:26,193
-Good luck, everybody.

29
00:01:26,193 --> 00:01:28,663
-I would like the team
to approve.

30
00:01:28,663 --> 00:01:30,861
-Thank you so much.

31
00:01:32,902 --> 00:01:35,079
-And the hat stays
on your head.

32
00:01:35,079 --> 00:01:38,652
-Connor Storrie!

